    "individual_blog_fLfQFq": {
      "type": "individual-blog",
      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_e4NGCi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When you buy jewelry, you pour your heart and soul into making sure it is something you absolutely love. Months later you find yourself putting it back into your jewelry box to protect it, to make sure its charm doesn’t chip away or tarnish. Now, you bring it out only for special occasions.</p><p>Exquisite jewelry shouldn’t be hidden away for special occasions, it should be worn everyday as a form of self-expression. And bezel settings are the perfect way to do it. Be it an exhilarating work out at the gym, a fun day at the theme park, or a day of much needed rest and relaxation, your bezel set ring will be right there with you sparking away.</p><p>Let’s break down why bezel-set jewelry is an ideal pick for a life in motion, and how it offers a sweatproof, snag-free, and sleep-safe experience you can rely on.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_8Xgrnx": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "What Is A Bezel Setting?",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/LJ-R00456YG_1F.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>What Is A Bezel Setting?</h2><p>A metal band surrounding your ring makes a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sports-collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Bezel Setting</span></a>. The band wraps around the perimeter of the diamond extending slightly over the diamond's edge. It makes sure that you as well as your diamond stays protected from chips and snags. </p><p>The Bezel Setting has been around for ages, but it has recently gained popularity because of its comfort and durability.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "what-is-a-bezel-setting",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_B9kX8c": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Fit For An Active Lifestyle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lucira_24-5-25_46085.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Fit For An Active Lifestyle</h2><p>All the adventure lovers out there need jewelry that can keep up with you. An active lifestyle means that your jewelry needs to hold up well with moisture, movement and skin contact. Unlike prong settings that have nooks and crannies where sweat and lotion can settle, bezels, with their smooth and sealed finish, are easier to clean and less prone to collecting grime. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "fit-for-an-active-lifestyle",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-40ct-half-eternity-pave-diamond-band",
              "0-4ct-emerald-round-toi-et-moi-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_h67LLU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Because a bezel setting surrounds the diamond completely, it offers better protection against everyday elements like sweat and natural skin oils. These substances can collect under traditional prongs, leading to buildup and potential dullness over time. With a bezel, there are fewer crevices for grime to hide, making it less prone to residue, and easier to clean when needed.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Jg3Qgr": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "No Holding Back",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Anatomy_of_a_Bezel_Setting_Components_Types_Durability_560_x_400_px_Inside_4th_Image_bb2b0e4d-9006-47ad-9dd7-cbfd84702335.png",
            "text": "<h2>No Holding Back: Snag-Free Confidence</h2><p>Bezel Settings make sure that snags don’t hold you back. With Bezel Setting Jewelry, your diamond sits in-line or slightly above the rim, but without sharp edges or corners sticking out. That means nothing gets caught on fabrics, towels, or even your own skin. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "no-holding-back-snag-free-confidence",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-21ct-half-eternity-diamond-band",
              "0-25-cts-classic-solitaire-diamond-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_4A6JB3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Whether you’re a new mother cherishing those fast paced moments with your baby or a business woman who needs to be in a million places at once, the flush edges of a bezel give you one less thing to worry about.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PnTCmB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Sleep Safe And Sound",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Sleep Safe And Sound</h2><p>If you’re one of the people who never take their rings off, even when you’re sleeping, then you need jewelry that keeps you safe and comfortable. No one wants to wake up with the shape of prongs imprinted on their face or with a bruise or a scratch. With regular pressure applied to your ring while sleeping, your stone can even come loose.  </p><p>That is why bezel-set rings are a great choice. The smooth metal frame means no sharp corners pressing into your skin, no prongs bending, and no stones digging into your skin. Since the diamond is held evenly around the edge, the pressure is distributed, and there’s less risk of pressure points or stress fractures forming over time. </p>",
            "custom_id": "sleep-safe-and-sound",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3hHxYb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Final Thoughts: Jewelry That Moves With You",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Final Thoughts: Jewelry That Moves With You</h2><p>At the end of the day, jewelry should fit into your life, not slow you down.</p><p>Bezel-set pieces offer a rare combination of practicality, durability, and beauty. They’re designed for people who want to live a full and dazzling life. They’re made for movement, for multitasking, for living freely.</p><p>If you’re looking for jewelry that keeps up through workouts, work days, and weekends, the bezel setting is more than just a style. It’s a solution.</p>",
            "custom_id": "final-thoughts-jewelry-that-moves-with-you",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
